# Goal
Perform a destructive review of the draft plan before implementation begins.

## Required inputs
- `docs/agentic-workflow/02_plan.md`
- `docs/agentic-workflow/01_context_pack.md`
- `docs/agentic-workflow/01c_architecture_overview.md` when present
- `docs/agentic-workflow/02a_architecture_review.md` when present

## Process
1. identify hidden assumptions
2. identify missing edge cases
3. identify unjustified complexity
4. identify scope-drift risk
5. identify architecture-plan mismatch when relevant
6. classify findings as blocking or non-blocking

## Output
Write the synthesis into `docs/agentic-workflow/03_plan_redteam.md`.
